name: CREAMY ROSE AND SWALLOWS CHARM NECKLACE
description:
CREAMY ROSE AND SWALLOWS CHARM NECKLACE

A creamy resin rose hanging on an antique goldtone chain  with two brass swallows flying down. Creamy rose measures 1 1/8" in diameter and the necklace measures 17 1/2" inches in length.

This necklace will come carefully wrapped in a red organza bag.

Postage and packing in the UK is included in the price.

name: TINY PERFUME BOTTLE AND SWALLOW CHARM NECKLACE - 2 colours
description:
TINY PERFUME BOTTLE AND SWALLOW CHARM NECKLACE

Tiny little glass perfume bottle, the top unscrews and you can put a couple of drops of scent inside. Hanging on a silvertone chain with a swallow flying down. Perfume bottle measures just under 1" from top t bottom and the necklace measures 25" inches in length.

This necklace will come carefully wrapped in a red organza bag.

Postage and packing in the UK are included in the price.

name: 3 BABY OWLS ON A BRANCH CHARM NECKLACE
description:
3 BABY OWLS ON A BRANCH CHARM NECKLACE

Brass charm of 3 baby owls on a branch with a goldtone chain. 3 owls charm measures 3/4 inch across and the necklace measures 17 inches in length.

This necklace will come carefully wrapped in a red organza bag.

Postage and packing in the UK are included in the price.

name: LARGE VINTAGE LOCKET AND CHAIN
description:
LARGE VINTAGE LOCKET AND CHAIN

Large vintage oval brass locket on a thick vintage brass chain. Locket opens to hold two photos and measures 1 3/4 x 1 1/2 inches and the chain measures 16 1/2 inches with a toggle clasp. thsi necklace is made of vintage pieces and will show signs of age.

This necklace will come carefully wrapped in a red organza bag.

Postage and packing in the UK are included in the price.

description:
"PLEASE LET ME OUT OF THIS BIRDCAGE" CHARM NECKLACE

Antique goldtone birdcage with a tiny bird peeping through the bars hanging on a fine 20" antique goldtone chain. birdcage charm measures 1 1/4 x 3/4 inch.

this necklace will come carefully wrapped in a red organza bag.

Postage and packing  in the UK is included in the price.
